title: Rosecrans wins sectional finals over Steubenville Catholic Central
text: Rosecrans wins sectional finals over Steubenville Catholic Central Buy Photo Rosecrans' Carter Hagy and Steubenville Catholic Central's Jacob Rigaud battle for possession during the Bishops 5-1 Division III sectional finals win over the Crusaders on Saturday in Zanesville.
